 achieved without trashing Birmingham&#8217;s history.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Download: <a href=\"https:\/\/zerocarbonhousebirmingham.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/IMG_1051-scaled.jpg\">Private Eye: Nooks and Corners<\/a>\u00a0(JPEG)<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sign our petition<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Please add your name to our petition to <a href=\"https:\/\/you.38degrees.org.uk\/petitions\/preserve-smallbrook-queensway-s-1960s-style-1?bucket=&amp;source=twitter-share-button\">Preserve Smallbrook Queensway\u2019s 1960s style<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Previous media coverage of the campaign<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/c20society.org.uk\/news\/alternative-plans-tabled-for-birminghams-threatened-ringway-centre\">Twentieth Century Society&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/a>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.architectsjournal.co.uk\/news\/anti-demolition-coalition-proposes-alternative-to-corstorphine-wrights-birmingham-plans\">Architects Journal<\/a>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bdonline.co.uk\/news\/stirling-prize-winners-back-bid-to-save-brutalist-landmark-in-brum\/5120745.article\">Building Design<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.birminghammail.co.uk\/news\/midlands-news\/battle-over-brutalist-buildings-birmingham-25643767\">Birmingham Live: Battle over brutalist buildings in Birmingham as open letter sent to council<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.birminghammail.co.uk\/news\/midlands-news\/ringway-centre-development-bring-bland-25677533\">Birmingham Live: Ringway Centre development will bring \u2018bland and overbearing mass\u2019 to Birmingham city centre<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The c